All Implemented Interfaces:
Path<Projection>
public class Projection
extends Path.PEntity<Projection>

Projection is a general safe projection from tables and subqueries. Use the projection class by subclassing it and adding the used columns like this : 

 class EmployeeProjection extends Projection{
     public EmployeeProjection(String entityName) {
         super(entityName);
     }
     Expr id;
     Expr firstname;
     Expr superiorId;
 }
